overview: Emma Hix and Kylie Rocket have been friends for a long time, but now that Emma's getting married Kylie is ready to deliver some sagely advice: that no woman should get married before trying girl-on-girl. Sophia Leone & Mae Milano, Aria Lee & Alexia Anders, and Gianna Dior & Izzy Lush are all inside taking charge of their sexuality.
title: Boss 2
